 859: #### Problem
 860: `updateFutureInstances()` in the recurring event handler makes two sequential `calendar.events.get()` calls for the same event:
 861: 1. First in `detectEventType()` to check if event is recurring
 862: 2. Second in `updateFutureInstances()` to get full event for split operation
