 872: 2. Updated `updateEventWithScope()` to call `getEventAndType()` instead of `detectEventType()`
 873: 3. Updated `updateFutureInstances()` signature to accept optional event parameter
 874: 4. Pass fetched event from routing method to `updateFutureInstances()` delegate
 875: 5. Delegate uses passed event instead of re-fetching
 876: 6. Maintained backward compatibility: if no event passed, method fetches it (for isolated test calls)
